data.description: Location location location!! - Welcome to Cayuga island on a very quiet, well maintained street. This 3 bedroom, 2 bath home has great curb appeal. Roof replaced in 2012. The home has central air, large 2 car detached garage plus a blacktop driveway with ample parking. Sept 2023 updates include: New luxury vinyl plank flooring (living room, kitchen, main floor hallway); new carpet in all 3 bedrooms, majority of main floor repainted. Main floor bathroom has new lighting, new vanity, new medicine cabinet mirror, paint and shower head. Basement bathroom has been painted, with new vinyl floor, new shower tile floor, new toilet and new shower head. Entire home air duct system has been cleaned and sanitized, new sump pump. Furnace was serviced and found to be in good working condition. Close to all amenities, beautiful park, and highway access. Don't miss out on this opportunity!
